ist production platforms that degrade ecosystems, accelerate global warming and exploit gendered and racialized bodies. We will do so by creating an archive of energy transition texts (stories, video, art, textiles, artefacts) produced through participatory action research; by analyzing how feminist ideas, narratives, digital media creations and social justice activism intersect with women's marginalized traditions and practices of social reproduction and common value creation on which the sustainability of households and communities depend; and by showing how practices of social reproduction are important for developing feminist strategies of communication and networks of cooperation, conscientization and repoliticization.","principal_investigator":"Sheena Wilson","principal_investigator_identifier":"0000-0002-8537-5252","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":4815,"title":"My plan (University of Alberta Template)","dmptemplate_id":1,"created_at":"2017-07-18 20:17:24 UTC","updated_at":"2017-07-18 20:17:24 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-alberta-template--601","organisation_id":1,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":4816,"title":"Mon plan (Modèle Portage)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2017-07-18 20:33:13 UTC","updated_at":"2017-07-18 20:33:13 UTC","slug":"mon-plan-modele-portage--142","organisation_id":29,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Julie Sergent","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":4817,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2017-07-19 18:00:43 UTC","updated_at":"2017-07-19 18:00:43 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1181","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Vivek Jadon","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"dat