ce, Map Promising Approaches to Care Relationships, Evaluative Innovative Practice, and Examine Policy Context. The study which employs diverse and multiple methods is being conducted in four Canadian provinces - British Columbia, Alberta, Ontario and Nova Scotia. SALTY results will have relevance for jurisdictions across Canada.\r\n","principal_investigator":"Janice Keefe","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"Lisa Tay lisa.tay@msvu.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":4833,"title":"NWT CIMP Data Collection","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2017-07-26 17:59:06 UTC","updated_at":"2017-07-27 14:53:51 UTC","slug":"nwt-cimp-data-collection","organisation_id":null,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"The NWT Cumulative Impact Monitoring Program conducts and funds research to help track cumulative effects on the environment.  The data from these projects, on water quality, vegetation, soils and sediments, and fish, will be used in decision making under regulatory review processes as well as available to the public on open access data portals.","principal_investigator":"Julian Kanigan","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"Chris Hotson","funder_name":null},{"id":4836,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2017-07-26 23:08:54 UTC","updated_at":"2017-07-26 23:08:54 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1197","organisation_id":26,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Dana Marlatt","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":4837,"title":"Mon plan (Modèle Portage) TEST - Écrire le même nom que dans la demande","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2017-07-27 17:28:08 UTC","updated_at":"2017-07-27 17:33:44 UTC","slug":"mon-plan-modele-portage-test-ecrire-le-meme-nom-que-dans-la-demande","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":"# de référence de la subvention si ce plan est suivant l'octroi","identifier":"TEST","description":"Ce