iew data management plan has been designed for Psych9560 and aims to answer the following research questions:\r\n\r\n1.\tWhat terms are being used to describe constructs of auditory temporal processes?\r\n2.\tHow are different constructs of auditory temporal processing being measured behaviourally?\r\n3.\tWhat terms and tasks align in describing/measuring constructs of auditory temporal processing and is there overlap in which constructs different terms and tasks describe and measure?\r\n\r\nData will be collected through literature searches and extraction will be performed to answer the research questions.","principal_investigator":"Rachael Smyth","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5510,"title":"My plan (University of Alberta Template)","dmptemplate_id":1,"created_at":"2018-03-05 17:47:43 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-05 17:47:43 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-alberta-template--648","organisation_id":1,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Lia Daniels","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5511,"title":"RDM Plan","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-05 20:54:06 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-05 20:54:34 UTC","slug":"rdm-plan","organisation_id":26,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"Matthew Gertler","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5512,"title":"Online Dating Study","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-05 21:52:55 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-05 21:53:58 UTC","slug":"online-dating-study","organisation_id":27,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"The broad purpose of this study is to establish how experiences of rejection on a (bogus) dating website impact mate choice, We also hope to examine the role of ideal partner standards and flexibility in mate choice on a dating website pre and post rejection. We also seek to explore whether these relationships are impacted by self-perceived mate value, self-esteem, and rejection sensitivity. Finally, we hope to establish whether reported ideal standards align with responses to purportedly public dating profile descriptions.","principal_investigator":"Nicolyn Charlot","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5513,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-05 21:55:23 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-05 21:55:23 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1616","organisation_id":27,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Joanne Paterson","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5514,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 12:47:13 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 12:47:13 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1617","organisation_id":24,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Alex Goudreau","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5515,"title":"Evaluating the effects of literacy-based language intervention on narrative language skills","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 14:28:14 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 14:29:37 UTC","slug":"evaluating-the-effects-of-literacy-based-language-intervention-on-narrative-language-skills","organisation_id":27,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"Current evidence suggests that narrative tasks involving sharing and retelling of stories are effective both for assessment and intervention in school age children with developmental language disorder. The present study examines the effectiveness of a literacy-based language intervention on narrative language skills, compared to a traditional teacher-consultation model of language intervention. Specifically, this study will examine sentence length, grammatical accuracy, and number of story elements recalled in children's retelling of short stories pre- and post-intervention.","principal_investigator":"Alexandra Cross","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5516,"title":"Test plan","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:15 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 17:22:12 UTC","slug":"test-plan--9","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"Here is a description of my plan. ","principal_investigator":"Michelle Dion","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5517,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:16 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:16 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1620","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Gerjan Altenburg","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5518,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:19 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:19 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1621","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"McMaster RDM","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5519,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:20 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:20 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1622","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"McMaster RDM","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5520,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:22 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-06 17:21:22 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1623","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":null,"identifie