le":"BCNRI: There & Back Again","dmptemplate_id":11,"created_at":"2018-03-07 00:43:15 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-07 00:53:17 UTC","slug":"bcnri-there-back-again","organisation_id":7,"grant_number":"MSFHR-BCNRI ","identifier":"","description":"This narrative study aims to document patient, family, and care providers' experiences of getting back to their rural community after receiving care at a referral centre. \r\n\r\nParticipants will be invited to share their story in an interview setting where a researcher uses a guide and semi-structured prompts to elicit their storied experience of getting back home. These interviews will be recorded on a digital recorder and later transcribed. The recordings and transcriptions are what constitute the data for the study. These data will be analyzed collaboratively in N-Vivo (a qualitative data analysis software program) by the research team, and then shared back with participants as composite stories (i.e., stories that are combined to reflect common experiences while protecting privacy and confidentiality). ","principal_investigator":"Katrina Plamondon","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5527,"title":"My plan (NRC Data Management Plan template)","dmptemplate_id":33,"created_at":"2018-03-07 13:35:14 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-07 13:35:14 UTC","slug":"my-plan-nrc-data-management-plan-template","organisation_id":39,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Chantal Ripp","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5528,"title":"Mon test (Modèle Portage)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-03-07 14:11:51 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-07 14:13:33 UTC","slug":"mon-test-modele-portage","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"Martine BARALE","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":5533,"title":"My plan (Por