mily-and-support-networks-for-those-living-with-hiv","organisation_id":null,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"The Purpose of this research is to provide information on the impact on non-professionals who care for and offer support to persons living with HIV. HIV is no longer considered to be a death sentence and the medications available allow those living with HIV to lead relatively normal lives. That being said, people living with HIV are at greater risk of sickness and may need support in various ways, such as social support and mental health support. The question for this research is, in what ways does being a friend, family member or part of a support network for a person living with HIV impact that person’s knowledge, perception’s and experience’s related to HIV?","principal_investigator":"A Schroeder","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"Alina.schroeder@unbc.ca, 2509605430","funder_name":null},{"id":5738,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-04-25 17:35:22 UTC","updated_at":"2018-04-25 17:35:22 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1776","organisation_id":23,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5739,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-04-26 13:18:06 UTC","updated_at":"2018-04-26 13:18:06 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--1777","organisation_id":13,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":5741,"title":"Test CNRC (NRC Data Management Plan template Draft)","dmptemplate_id":33,"created_at":"2018-04-26 14:46:11 UTC","updated_at":"2018-04-26 14:47:02 UTC","slug":"test-cnrc-nrc-data-management-plan-template-draft","organisation_id":39,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","prin