ue of donated textiles, these funds may be sufficient to launch and maintain a skills training program. ","principal_investigator":"Jennifer Wright","principal_investigator_identifier":"Meredith Jones","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":6607,"title":"My plan (University of Alberta Template)","dmptemplate_id":1,"created_at":"2018-10-31 15:44:40 UTC","updated_at":"2018-10-31 15:44:40 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-alberta-template--704","organisation_id":1,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Olga Gonzalez","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":6608,"title":"Are Smart Cities Healthy?","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2018-10-31 16:03:44 UTC","updated_at":"2019-02-25 19:14:17 UTC","slug":"are-smart-cities-healthy","organisation_id":23,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"How do you measure a Smart City?\r\n\r\nUsing publicly available Stats Can data, create a city level database of Canadian cities that contains demographics, economic, governance, transportation, etc. \r\n\r\nWorking in RDC using microdata, looking at relationship between employment and health.\r\n\r\nMerging the two for multilevel modeling.","principal_investigator":"Jenny Godley","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"jgodley@ucalgary.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":6609,"title":"My plan (OMAFRA-UG Agreement Template)","dmptemplate_id":45,"created_at":"2018-10-31 17:37:58 UTC","updated_at":"2018-10-31 17:37:58 UTC","slug":"my-plan-omafra-ug-agreement-template--12","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":6610,"title":"My plan (OMAFRA-UG Agreement Template)","dmptemplate_id":45,"created_at":"2018-10-31 18:22:02 UTC","updated_at":"2018-10-31 18:22:02 UTC","slug":"my-plan-omafra-ug-agreement-template--13","organisation_id"