y everyone or that are focused on users with specific preferences (e.g., competition vs collaboration, goal-oriented vs open-ended gameplay, fast-paced vs relaxed experiences, etc.).","principal_investigator":"Gustavo Tondello","principal_investigator_identifier":"0000-0002-4174-7245","data_contact":"Gustavo Tondello","funder_name":null},{"id":7560,"title":"Trial ALES (University of Alberta Template)","dmptemplate_id":1,"created_at":"2019-06-06 22:06:31 UTC","updated_at":"2019-06-06 22:08:57 UTC","slug":"trial-ales-university-of-alberta-template","organisation_id":1,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"Brett Finch","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":7561,"title":"Data Management Plan - PSYC6670","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-06-07 15:35:46 UTC","updated_at":"2019-06-07 15:39:36 UTC","slug":"data-management-plan-psyc6670","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"I am investigating whether interview anxiety relates to job performance in a sample of undergraduate co-operative education students. I propose a relationship will exist when the moderating effects of cognitive ability and social-evaluative job content are taken in consideration. The data will be collected for my Master's thesis. ","principal_investigator":"Deborah Powell","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"Irene Zhang, 519-661-8632, izhang@uoguelph.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":7562,"title":"MA Thesis Plan (PSYC*6670)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-06-07 15:52:56 UTC","updated_at":"2019-06-07 15:54:11 UTC","slug":"ma-thesis-plan-psyc-6670","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"The purpose of this plan is to consider data management for my MA thesis project, as part of the PSYC*6670 Research Methods Class.","principal_investigator":"Baylee Rubinoff","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{