ge-template--2772","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":"","identifier":"0859824","description":"Researchers will be conducting a policy-capturing study using a Qualtrics Online Sample. The research question is as follow: How do targets’ individual differences and \r\nenactors’ resources influence enactors’ propensity to omit a behavior that can be perceived as uncivil?\r\n\r\nThe data will be collected in order to answer this research question and to test whether individuals who are higher on negative traits (e.g., anxiety, depression, neuroticism) are more likely to be targeted by enactors of incivility. The collection of the data will also lead to the completion of a Master's thesis.\r\n","principal_investigator":"Yannick Provencher/Dr. M. Gloria Gonzalez-Morales","principal_investigator_identifier":"0859824","data_contact":"Dr. M. Gloria Gonzalez-Morales; mggonzal@uoguelph.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":7604,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-06-14 01:21:54 UTC","updated_at":"2019-06-14 01:21:54 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--2773","organisation_id":null,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Rachel Sue-A-Quan","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":7605,"title":"My plan (University of Guelph Agri-Food Funding Template (Alliance/Food from Thought) )","dmptemplate_id":45,"created_at":"2019-06-14 13:39:16 UTC","updated_at":"2019-06-14 13:39:16 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-guelph-agri-food-funding-template-alliance-food-from-thought--11","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Carol Perry","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":7606,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-06-14 14:15:40 UTC","updated_at":"2019-06-14 14:15:40 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--2774","organis