bile robotics, vision sensing, and AI systems equipped with machine learning and algorithms to estimate the number of flowers and fruit size of developing apples, which will transform the precision at which apples can be managed.  To achieve this, images of flowers and fruit will be taken by a specialized camera and will be used by our algorithms to determine the number of flowers per tree and fruit size to predict yield and help manage the crop. Part of the images taken will be used for training of the algorithms and the rest will be used for verification. ","principal_investigator":"John Cline","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"(519) 426-7127 x331, jcline@uoguelph.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":7843,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-08-29 03:34:19 UTC","updated_at":"2019-08-29 03:35:01 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--2884","organisation_id":23,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"lei wang","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":7844,"title":"Compostable Thermoformed Vegetable Packaging from Ontario Waste Starch","dmptemplate_id":45,"created_at":"2019-08-29 14:10:07 UTC","updated_at":"2019-08-29 14:15:30 UTC","slug":"compostable-thermoformed-vegetable-packaging-from-ontario-waste-starch","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":"030416","identifier":"LAAIR2019-5380","description":"This technology will produce thermoformed compostable mushroom packages with comparable mechanical and barrier performance to conventional version in the market.","principal_investigator":"Amar Mohanty","principal_investigator_identifier":"0000-0002-1079-2481","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":7845,"title":"Mon plan (Modèle Portage)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-08-29 18:42:55 UTC","updated_at":"2019-08-29 18:42:55 UTC","slug":"mon-plan-modele-portage--408","organisation_id":11,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"descrip