dentified electors. At level of polling/voting areas, includes turnout and candidate vote share data based on provincial elections data; also associated demographic data (e.g., household income, education, etc.)\r\n\r\nData collected from sources including provincial/territorial electoral maps, electoral results, Census of Canada, together with considerable original coding by study author.","principal_investigator":"Karen Bird","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":7938,"title":"C3 Evaluation","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-09-13 15:42:26 UTC","updated_at":"2019-09-13 15:50:12 UTC","slug":"c3-evaluation","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"This study is focused on evaluating the success of the C3 backbone organization in significantly increasing the success of youth taking on employment in Hamilton, Ontario.  The primary purpose is to improve the program's work and to support replication in other settings.  There is also potential that this effort will serve to inform policy around other programs, so to the extent the data can be available to frame policy consideration is key.  ","principal_investigator":"Allison Van","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"289-244-5479, allisvan@gmail.com","funder_name":null},{"id":7939,"title":"Test1","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-09-13 15:42:36 UTC","updated_at":"2019-09-13 15:42:54 UTC","slug":"test1--2","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"Max Stick","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":7940,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-09-13 15:43:00 UTC","updated_at":"2019-09-13 15:43:00 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--2938","organisation_id":10,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Sam McDonald","principal_investigator_identifier"