ics for uncovering biomarkers for non-alcoholic fatty liver disease.\r\n\r\nThe research questions addressed will be are there any additional biomarkers that can be used to screen for the disease that would be an alternative to an invasive biopsy.\r\n\r\nThe data collected from serum samples will be analyzed and used to uncover these biomarkers.","principal_investigator":"Ritchie Ly","principal_investigator_identifier":"Philip Britz-McKibbin","data_contact":"britz@mcmaster.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":8204,"title":"My plan (UVic DMP Template)","dmptemplate_id":44,"created_at":"2019-10-22 17:54:58 UTC","updated_at":"2019-10-22 17:54:58 UTC","slug":"my-plan-uvic-dmp-template--49","organisation_id":21,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Jack Lawson","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8205,"title":"Quality Assurance Higher Ed Ecuador","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-10-22 18:08:41 UTC","updated_at":"2019-10-22 18:09:38 UTC","slug":"quality-assurance-higher-ed-ecuador","organisation_id":27,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"Diego Sornoza","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":8206,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-10-22 18:10:21 UTC","updated_at":"2019-10-22 18:10:21 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3084","organisation_id":27,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Elizabeth  elizabeth.minda@uwo.ca","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8207,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-10-22 18:10:35 UTC","updated_at":"2019-10-22 18:10:35 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3085","organisation_id":27,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Wenyu Huang","principal_inve