everance-policies","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":"UofG2017-2924","identifier":"","description":"Measurement of Farmland Loss using a process whereby Official Plan amendments are tracked to identify changes early in the development process.","principal_investigator":"Wayne Caldwell","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"Wayne Caldwell","funder_name":null},{"id":8399,"title":"Mon plan (Modèle Portage)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-11-07 22:14:20 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-07 22:14:20 UTC","slug":"mon-plan-modele-portage--454","organisation_id":53,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Jonathan Dorey","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8400,"title":"My plan (University of Alberta Template)","dmptemplate_id":1,"created_at":"2019-11-07 23:38:32 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-07 23:38:32 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-alberta-template--771","organisation_id":1,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"yiheng6@ualberta.ca","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8401,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-11-08 12:15:14 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-08 12:15:14 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3168","organisation_id":null,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Shukri F Mohamed","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8402,"title":"CPTP CANUE External Data","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-11-08 15:19:52 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-08 17:53:00 UTC","slug":"cptp-canue-external-data","organisation_id":20,"grant_number":"","identifier":"CANUE","description":"The supplementary agreement to the DMSA that OICR signed with CPAC, which was subsequently assigned to U of T, describes CANUE data as follows:\r\nThe Canadian Urban Environmental Health Research Consortium gathers and develops measures of environmental factors for every neighbourhood across Canada. The datasets include variables related to multiple characteristics of urban form, such as air and noise pollution, land use, transportation, physical infrastructure, and socioeconomic conditions.\r\nCANUE data will be linked to all CPTP core baseline questionnaire, the Harmonized Dataset.\r\n  \r\nCANUE build a data platform for etiologic, measurement and intersectoral prevention research. Data on characteristics of urban form, such as air and noise pollution, land use, transportation, physical infrastructure and socioeconomic conditions that have separately been linked to health impacts or benefits were collected to respond to how these exposures interact to affect health and how this changes over time and place.","principal_investigator":"https://canue.ca/leadership-and-staff/#executive","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"CPTP AO","funder_name":null},{"id":8403,"title":"My plan (Ocean Data Management Plan)","dmptemplate_id":28,"created_at":"2019-11-08 16:39:54 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-08 16:39:54 UTC","slug":"my-plan-ocean-data-management-plan--120","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Semra Yalcin","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8404,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2019-11-08 19:50:16 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-08 19:50:16 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3170","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":8406,"title":"My plan (University of Manitoba )","dmptemplate_id":35,"created_at":"2019-11-09 01:11:40 UTC","updated_at":"2019-11-09 01:11:40 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-manitoba--48","organisation_id"