o. A variety of field measurements will be performed at the Elora Research Station to better understand nitrogen and phosphorus leaching in Ontario soils with tillage, compaction, applied manure and cover crops. During years 1 and 2, soil water content, nutrient concentrations and isotopic ratios will be measured at multiple depths across different soil plots. In year 3, blue dye will be applied to the soil plots, which will be subsequently excavated to visualize soil water flow pathways. The end products of this project will be data-driven model simulations that will be used to conceptualize dominant water and nutrient movement dynamics.","principal_investigator":"Genevieve Ali","principal_investigator_identifier":"0000-0001-5144-8188","data_contact":"gali@uoguelph.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":9294,"title":"My plan (University of Alberta Template)","dmptemplate_id":1,"created_at":"2020-06-16 22:33:14 UTC","updated_at":"2020-06-16 22:33:14 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-alberta-template--844","organisation_id":1,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Suzette Bremault-Phillips","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":9295,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-06-16 23:30:53 UTC","updated_at":"2020-06-16 23:30:53 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3619","organisation_id":22,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"carson balestreri","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":9296,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-06-17 12:58:40 UTC","updated_at":"2020-06-17 12:58:40 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3620","organisation_id":12,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Éthel Gamache","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},