 we would like to develop in future. In brief, these needs and preferences will inform our system’s development. \r\n","principal_investigator":"Samira Rahimi","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"Neda Parinejad, neda.parinejadkhameneh@mcgill.ca","funder_name":null},{"id":9775,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-10-22 19:56:45 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-22 19:56:45 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3854","organisation_id":8,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":9776,"title":"GEOE 446/447 - IBM","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-10-22 20:13:10 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-22 20:17:46 UTC","slug":"geoe-446-447-ibm","organisation_id":33,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"This project aims to discover if and how machine learning can be used in mineral exploration. It will focus on the identification of key minerals in drill core data using XRF and imaging. ","principal_investigator":"Anya Jacksteit, Greg Stanhope, Adam Gordon, Connor Ibach","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":9777,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-10-23 15:35:53 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-23 15:35:53 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3856","organisation_id":25,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Richard Grant","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":9778,"title":"Mon plan (Université de Montréal (FR))","dmptemplate_id":43,"created_at":"2020-10-24 12:07:57 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-24 12:12:52 UTC","slug":"mon-plan-universite-de-montreal-fr--112","organisation_id":32,"grant_number":"","identifier":"","description":"","principal_investigator":"Lyne Da Sylva","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact