globulin for 4 consecutive days, and the placebo group will receive an equivalent volume of sodium chloride 0.9% for the same duration. The primary outcome is the number of ventilator-free days up to the 28th day. Secondary objectives are to evaluate the effect of IVIG  on organ failure according to the SOFA score at 14 and 28 days,  lung injury score at 14 and 28 days, the occurrence of grade 3 or 4 adverse events of IVIG  length of ICU stay, length of hospital stay, functional outcomes at 90 days defined by the activities of daily living and instrumental activities of the daily living scales and  90 days survival. 138 subjects will be randomized in a 1:1 ratio to IVIG or placebo groups (69 in each group), considering 90% power, alpha level 0.05 (two sides), and 0.67 effect size level. ","principal_investigator":"Aurélien Mazeraud","principal_investigator_identifier":"0000-0001-8473-7779","data_contact":"r.mancusi@ghu-paris.fr","funder_name":null},{"id":9788,"title":"My plan (Portage Template)","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-10-28 16:25:42 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-28 16:25:42 UTC","slug":"my-plan-portage-template--3861","organisation_id":23,"grant_number":null,"identifier":null,"description":null,"principal_investigator":"Derrick Rancourt","principal_investigator_identifier":null,"data_contact":null,"funder_name":null},{"id":9789,"title":"AI-assisted rule out of COVID-19","dmptemplate_id":12,"created_at":"2020-10-28 18:28:42 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-28 20:05:59 UTC","slug":"ai-assisted-rule-out-of-covid-19","organisation_id":13,"grant_number":"","identifier":"2021-2631","description":"","principal_investigator":"Artem Luhovy","principal_investigator_identifier":"","data_contact":"","funder_name":null},{"id":9790,"title":"My plan (University of British Columbia Generic Template)","dmptemplate_id":11,"created_at":"2020-10-29 00:01:21 UTC","updated_at":"2020-10-29 00:01:21 UTC","slug":"my-plan-university-of-british-columbia-generic-template--609","organisa